WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.133 --> 00:00:02.600
If the Empress likes it,

2
00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:04.766
I’ll come and attend to you every day.

3
00:00:05.333 --> 00:00:07.700
I have Wang Momo to serve you.

4
00:00:07.700 --> 00:00:09.966
The one who should be served is the Emperor.

5
00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:13.233
The Emperor only visits the Consort Xian.

6
00:00:13.533 --> 00:00:15.833
Now, the entire harem

7
00:00:16.300 --> 00:00:18.166
is under Noble Consort Long’s rule.

8
00:00:18.166 --> 00:00:19.766
Sister, don’t speak recklessly.

9
00:00:20.366 --> 00:00:22.633
It’s only because we’re powerless.

10
00:00:22.966 --> 00:00:26.033
This妖妃 (demon consort) is simply the second Noble Consort Yan.

11
00:00:28.266 --> 00:00:30.200
Quick, summon the imperial physician!

12
00:00:31.866 --> 00:00:34.066
Empress Dowager, are you alright?

13
00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:41.966
Mother, how are you?

14
00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:43.400
Your Majesty need not worry.

15
00:00:43.400 --> 00:00:46.733
The imperial physician says the Empress Dowager only had a moment of extreme anxiety.

16
00:00:46.733 --> 00:00:48.100
There’s nothing serious.

17
00:00:48.666 --> 00:00:49.466
Your Majesty,

18
00:00:52.766 --> 00:00:54.833
Mother, are you alright?

19
00:00:57.133 --> 00:00:58.666
I’m fine.

20
00:00:59.766 --> 00:01:00.700
But I am unfilial.

21
00:01:01.066 --> 00:01:02.266
Recently, with all the affairs,

22
00:01:02.333 --> 00:01:03.600
I haven’t been visiting you enough.

23
00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:04.500
Mother,

24
00:01:05.600 --> 00:01:08.566
Recently, it has been Noble Consort De coming to pay her respects.

25
00:01:09.066 --> 00:01:11.433
I only hope the six palaces remain harmonious.

26
00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:13.600
I also know,

27
00:01:13.933 --> 00:01:16.000
you have a strong liking for Noble Consort Rong.

28
00:01:16.300 --> 00:01:19.200
But too much of anything is excessive.

29
00:01:19.533 --> 00:01:24.000
The Emperor should still be fair to all.

30
00:01:29.966 --> 00:01:31.066
I will make my own decisions.

31
00:01:31.566 --> 00:01:32.800
Don’t worry, Mother.

32
00:01:37.766 --> 00:01:38.700
Thank you for your concern.

33
00:01:39.766 --> 00:01:40.900
Your Majesty.
